data.description: This very spacious 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home, sitting on a half acre lot and located in the highly sought after PNGISD, does need a little TLC but would be perfect for a growing family! This home offers two separate living areas with a large living room downstairs, as well as a living room upstairs, that would make for a great play or lounge area. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel stove and dishwasher, tile floors and plenty of cabinets for storage. The master bedroom is downstairs with a private bathroom and direct access onto the covered back patio that overlooks the massive backyardl! This is a lot of home for the money and would make for a great long term investment so don't miss your chance to call it home. Text or call your favorite realtor and schedule your showing today!
